title: The Cheech And Chong Collection XviD
description:
Hey, it's Doob-O-Clock
Sometime last year SoSISO did a bunch of Cheech and Chong Movies.
I scooped them all and have put them on one disc.
Up in Smoke, Next Movie, Nice Dreams, Things are Tough All Over, Still Smoking and Corsican Brothers.
Its nearly their entire filmography (except Yellowbeard).
Enjoy your favourite C + C done with TDX2005 rules.
Here's the stats.
